    supports HTML5 video This is a modal window. Beginning of dialog window. Escape will cancel and close the window. End of dialog window. USewpersad uthe ngenkathi kuqhubeka imibhikisho kulimale amaphoyisa amabili uConstable Eugene Naidoo oshaywe ngetshe esiphomgweni noConstable Jerry Govender olinyazwe ngetshe eqolo. “Womabili amaphoyisa athole usizo lwezempilo kodwa uGovender ubuyele emsebenzini emva kokuxilongwa ngabezempilo”. USewpersad uthe kubizwe amaphoyisa ukuba azoqapha isimo ebusuku njengoba umbhikisho uqhubeke cishe usuku lonke. “Isimo sesidambile njengamanje kodwa amaphoyisa asaqaphile kule ndawo”.  